_sText:
Stone Palace 2 is an intense arena map with 2 bomb sites full of places to run, hide, snipe and die! This map runs very good and is a great addition to a servers map rotation. Any advice and thoughts for stone palace 3 will be welcomed. Enjoy the map!

Also, may I refer you to de_rooftops, it is another great map made by S_I_S_S_Y!
